    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mantles with a sleeve cut all in one with the side piece and hanging loose; sometimes made in the form of a sling.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
